<br>
Regardless, EVERYONE should attend at least one of each Vs Vox and Naggy.  I have been to several dragon raids with Ravilicus, and recently a few with Thunderbumm.  I have never won anything but the experiences have been some of the more interesting if for no other reason than fighting a dragon kicks ass.<br>
<br>
These days with Aegolism, C3, Circle Buffs, Elemental blankets, melee twink weapon upgrades and whatnot these raids are really much easier!  The Fed should definately host a raid sometime soon, especially if we can get some high level support for clearing giants, etc.  A Cleric with a click stick can often turn the tide in a battle with combat resses, too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#70DB93>- </font><a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/bfederationofpovar>Federation of Povar</a><font color=#70DB93> - </font><a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3>Federation Raid Ideas</a> <font color=#70DB93> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.0.91<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.<br>Accelerated By <a href=http://www.wbs.com/ezboard.html>JXEL</a></center></body></html>  

